---
// No props needed for static workflow
---
<section aria-label="How It Works" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-10 text-brand-dark">How It Works</h2>
  <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition group">
      <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-brand-red/10 group-hover:bg-brand-red/20">
        <!-- Chat/Consultation SVG -->
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M21 12c0 4-4.03 7-9 7a9.77 9.77 0 01-4-.8L3 20l1.1-3.3A7.98 7.98 0 013 12c0-4 4.03-7 9-7s9 3 9 7z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold mb-2">Consultation</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Understand your business needs and define success.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition group">
      <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-brand-orange/10 group-hover:bg-brand-orange/20">
        <!-- Integration SVG -->
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 17l4 4 4-4m0-5V3m-8 6v6a4 4 0 004 4h4"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold mb-2">Integration</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Seamless AI integration into your existing workflows.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition group">
      <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow/10 group-hover:bg-brand-yellow/20">
        <!-- Annotation SVG -->
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-yellow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.862 3.487a2.06 2.06 0 112.915 2.914L7.5 18.678l-4 1 1-4 13.362-13.19z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold mb-2">Annotation</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Expert data labeling and quality assurance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition group">
      <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-brand-dark/10 group-hover:bg-brand-dark/20">
        <!-- Support SVG -->
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18.364 5.636A9 9 0 105.636 18.364 9 9 0 0018.364 5.636zM9 10h.01M15 10h.01M12 14h.01"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold mb-2">Ongoing Support</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Continuous improvement and enterprise-grade support.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 